trans-unit.source: Exposes <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"></xref> control types to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Elérhetővé teszi <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"> </xref> típusok szabályozása [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The DocumentAutomationPeer represents documents and supports the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.
trans-unit.target: A DocumentAutomationPeer dokumentumok jelöli, és támogatja a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: Objects such as a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> can contain embedded objects, such as images and hyperlinks.
trans-unit.target: Objektumok, például egy <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>vagy <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>tartalmazhat beágyazott objektumok, például képek és hiperhivatkozások vegyes használatát.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>

trans-unit.source: Initially, when you try to get the child elements of the document, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> does not return the embedded objects.
trans-unit.target: Kezdetben, amikor megkísérli lekérni a gyermek a dokumentum elemek <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>nem ad vissza a beágyazott objektumokat.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To get the embedded elements, obtain a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> from the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> and call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Ahhoz, hogy a beágyazott elemek, szerezzen be egy <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>, és hívja meg <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>

trans-unit.source: After <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is called, any elements in that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> are returned by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Miután <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>nevezik, az adott <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> által visszaadott</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> elemeket</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Unless you know the document is a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, you should not call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Csak ha tudja, hogy a dokumentum van egy <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, nem hívja a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>a a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName>tulajdonság.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>

trans-unit.source: If the document is loaded from a network location, calling <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the entire document is resource intensive.
trans-unit.target: A dokumentum be van töltve, egy hálózati helyről, ha hívása <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>a teljes dokumentum van erőforrás intenzív.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>

trans-unit.source: Instead, you should use one of the methods on <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> that returns a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> that represents a portion of the document.
trans-unit.target: Ehelyett használja a módszerek <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>, amely adja vissza egy <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>, amely jelzi, hogy a dokumentum egy részét.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: This property does not indicate whether the element is visible.

trans-unit.source: In some circumstances, an element is on the screen but is still not visible.
trans-unit.target: Bizonyos körülmények között az elem a képernyőn, de még mindig nem látható.

trans-unit.target: Például ha az elem által egyéb elemek van látható, akkor visszatéréskor nem jelenik.

trans-unit.source: In this case, the method returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: Ebben az esetben a metódus visszaadja `false`.
